    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my reliable ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been so dependable for me! Whether you're commuting to work or heading out on a road trip, this car handles beautifully and still looks great on the road. It\u2019s been well-cared for and is ready to hit the pavement with a new owner. Come check it out\u2014you\u2019re going to love how it drives!",
