      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 35
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride, and I think you\u2019re going to love it! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. It\u2019s been well-loved and well-maintained, so while it has a little bit of character from being out on the road, it still looks sharp and runs like a dream. This is the perfect set of wheels if you're looking for something reliable and ready to go without any fuss. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
      "price": 31500.0,
